text.tspan: Upon learning about the administrative assistant posting with Wallace Design Collective, I was eager to
contact you with my interest. When reviewing the job description, I was excited to see how well my
experience aligns with your company's needs and position requirements. From reading your company's
website, I feel your core mission and culture suit what I offer as a professional as well.
As an adept secretary, I have a well-rounded set of skills in customer service and office administration. I
also honed my talents in data entry, multiline phone operation and scheduling. I am a recognized expert in
supply ordering, scheduling, database management and precise notetaking with a 70 WPM typing speed.
These abilities helped me increase office productivity by 60% and promote client satisfaction.
I am excited at the prospect of bringing my talents to Wallace Design Collective. I look forward to hearing
from you at your earliest convenience to discuss how my experience and qualifications will prove
valuable in the administrative assistant role.
Thank you for your time and consideration.
